            "title": "盤中速報 - 數據狗(DDOG-US)大漲9.25%，報147.5美元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>數據狗(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:DDOG:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/DDOG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">DDOG-US</a>)截至台北時間03日21:30股價上漲12.49美元，報147.50美元，漲幅9.25%，成交量1,803,679（股），盤中最高價147.56美元、最低價147.35美元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：+0.32%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：+0.47%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：+0.55%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：+0.45%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>數據狗(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:DDOG:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/DDOG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">DDOG-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：+3.19%</li> <li>近 1 月：+14.67%</li> <li>近 3 月：+32.74%</li> <li>近 6 月：-6%</li> <li>今年以來：-5.51%</li></ul></section></main>",
