        {
            "id": 6049625,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 新思科技(SNPS-US)大漲5.14%，報549.97美元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>新思科技(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:SNPS:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/SNPS\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">SNPS-US</a>)截至台北時間03日21:31股價上漲26.86美元，報549.97美元，漲幅5.14%，成交量124,571（股），盤中最高價550.00美元、最低價541.55美元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：+0.29%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：+0.47%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：+0.61%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：+0.68%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>新思科技(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:SNPS:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/SNPS\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">SNPS-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：+9.21%</li> <li>近 1 月：+12.22%</li> <li>近 3 月：+19.28%</li> <li>近 6 月：+8.36%</li> <li>今年以來：+7.78%</li></ul></section></main>",
